---
title: Panko-Crusted Mahi Mahi with Wasabi Aioli, Quinoa, and Green Bean-Tomato Saute
description: Pungent wasabi gives a nice little kick to the delicate, mild flavor of mahi mahi. A simple veggie saute completes this light and healthy weeknight dinner.
